rows.label: qst200817_msg0001
rows.name:
Get outta the way!
Or I'll make you regret it!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0002
rows.name:
Puttin' out fires we went and set?
I'll show you!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0003
rows.name:
No more!
You won't burn any more trees!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0004
rows.name:
Shut your filthy gob!
This has nothin' to do with you!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0005
rows.name: Move, or I'll make you move!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0006
rows.name:
The Saffronia trees are important
for the people of Fons Maim!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0007
rows.name:
We won't let you hurt
the trees anymore!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0008
rows.name:
Stop your yammerin'!
Someone get them outta my face!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0009
rows.name:
We're Invidians, born and bred!
We've all had combat training!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0010
rows.name:
If you punks think you can go
through us, just you ruddy try!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0012
rows.name:
I never knew so many people
cared about the outdoors...

rows.label: qst200817_msg0014
rows.name:
Sure!
I'll join this struggle gladly!
